<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pernicious" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pernicious,</orth> mischievous, malicious, wicked: <cit><quote>most p. purpose,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 2.4.150" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 4, 150</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this p. caitiff deputy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 5.88.150" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 88</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou p. woman,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 5.88.150" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 88</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>this p. slave,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 5.241" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 241</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>troubled with a p. suitor,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.130" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 130</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the p. and indubitate beggar Zenelophon,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.1.66" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 1, 66</bibl></cit> (Armado's letter). <cit><quote>thy adverse p. enemy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.82" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 82</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your p. lives,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 3.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 4</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to rid the realm of this p. blot,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 4.325.4" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 325</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you p. ass,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.2.80" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 2, 80</bibl></cit> (Q <emph>virtuous</emph>). <cit><quote>a most p. usurer,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 17</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your p. faction,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.59" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 59</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>p. protector,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.1.21" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 1, 21</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>p. bloodsucker,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.226" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 226</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>may prove p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.19" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 19</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your p. rage,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.1.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 1, 91</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this p. hour,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.133" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 1, 133</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with more p. root,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.85" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 85</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O most p. woman!</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.5.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 5, 105</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>two p. daughters,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 3.2.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 2, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his p. soul,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.155" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 155</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O the p. caitiff,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.155" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 155</bibl></cit>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>